law.history: Repealed 2002 Ky. Acts ch. 283, sec. 20, effective July 15, 2002; amended 2002 Ky. Acts ch. 183, sec. 8, effective August 1, 2002. -- Amended 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 491, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1998. -- Amended 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 395, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1994. -- Created 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 309, sec. 2, effective July 1, 1978.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Moneys from indigent defendants credited to fund of county where trial held -- Use -- Administrative fee assessed on persons for whom counsel is provided.
metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/2002). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 2002 Ky. Acts ch. 283 prevails over its amendment in 2002 Ky. Acts ch. 183.
